
'''Hodology''' is the study of pathways.  Not listed in the [[Oxford English Dictionary]], this [[neologism|recently created word]] is used in several different contexts.

#In [[brain]] physiology, it is the study of the interconnections of brain cells.
#In [[philosophy]], it is the study of interconnected [[idea]]s.
#In [[geography]], it is the study of [[path]]s.

